    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育平台画一个架构图，核心是内容分发和学生数据管理。先确定三个主要入口：BYOD设备、AVD虚拟桌面，还有后台的CTRL控制节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BYOD",
        "AVD",
        "CTRL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，BYOD是学生自带设备，AVD是学校的虚拟桌面门户，CTRL是学生数据库。那数据平面部分怎么组织？需要区分不同的网关通道吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DATA_PLANE",
        "GW1_LANE",
        "GW2_LANE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，数据平面要分成两条通道。GW1_LANE走LMS门户的流量，里面放DOMAIN、DEV、SEG三个服务节点。GW2_LANE走学生数据库相关的，放DOMSVC、DEVSVC、HWIL。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GW1_LANE",
        "GW2_LANE",
        "DOMAIN",
        "DEV",
        "SEG",
        "DOMSVC",
        "DEVSVC",
        "HWIL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，GW1_LANE和GW2_LANE都作为DATA_PLANE的子图，方向都是TB纵向排列。那GW1和GW2这两个网关节点本身要放在哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GW1",
        "GW2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GW1放在GW1_LANE顶部，GW2放在GW2_LANE顶部。AVD要同时连到两个网关，CTRL也要连两个网关，形成交叉备份。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GW1",
        "GW2",
        "AVD",
        "CTRL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加交叉连接。BYOD到AVD走Internet，AVD和CTRL到两个网关都是tcp/udp 443加udp 53。接下来画网关到内部服务的连接？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BYOD",
        "AVD",
        "CTRL",
        "GW1",
        "GW2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，GW1到DOMAIN、DEV、SEG都是全端口开放。GW2到DOMSVC、DEVSVC、HWIL也是全端口。这些内部服务之间不直接通信，全部经过网关。",
      "elements_involved": [
